      • findIssues

        public void findIssues()
        Perform the Issues & Solutions search. This opens a list of pending issues, i.e. it does not directly affect the table model. Pending issues will only be made visible when publishIssues() is called.

      • add

        public boolean add​(Solutions.Issue issue)
        Adds the issue to the list of pending issues that findIssues() has opened. This should only be called from inside {@link #Subject.findIssues(Solutions)}
        Parameters:
        issue -
        Returns:
        true if the issue was already marked as solved.

      • publishIssues

        public void publishIssues()
        Publish the pending issues that findIssues() has found i.e. that were added using add(Issue). This makes them visible trough the TableModel of this.
